Genesis 49, 10, predicted the scepter will not depart from Judah, and Jesus descends from the tribe of Judah.

23:25.594 --> 23:28.978
Most importantly, the timing of Messiah's arrival was given

23:29.154 --> 23:39.869
in Daniel chapter nine, verses 25 to 26, which predicted the Messiah's coming after 69 biblical sevens from the decree to rebuild Jerusalem.

23:40.370 --> 23:46.298
That calculated to be 483 years aligning with the life and times of Jesus.

23:47.259 --> 23:58.034
All of these prophecies interlock, the Virgin Born Emmanuel, the branch from Jesse, the Bethlehem ruler, the sun called out of Egypt, the Nazarene, all in one person.

23:58.562 --> 24:00.024
Reflect with me for a moment.

24:00.164 --> 24:06.013
Skeptics might say these prophecies were coincidences or somehow they were retrofitted.

24:06.613 --> 24:16.327
But consider the odds, specific places, events, characteristics, fulfilled altogether in one person associated with all of the locales I've mentioned.

24:16.808 --> 24:19.752
It's improbable without divine intervention.

24:20.393 --> 24:23.538
The Gospel writers Matthew and Luke did not invent all of this.

24:24.038 --> 24:26.642
They reported history through prophetic lenses.

24:26.914 --> 24:31.840
Early Christians, facing persecution, staked their faith on these prophetic fulfillments.

24:32.520 --> 24:43.673
And today, our busy holidays, these prophecies remind us that Messiah's birth is rooted in truth, not myth, but history prophesied and realized.

24:44.654 --> 24:47.998
As lights twinkle and carols play, ponder the puzzle thoroughly.

24:48.638 --> 24:51.101
God spoke through prophets, then acted in history.

24:51.982 --> 24:55.346
Jesus was Bethlehem's baby, Egypt's refugee,

24:55.490 --> 24:56.832
and Nazareth's branch.

24:57.333 --> 24:59.317
He is the centerpiece of history.

25:00.198 --> 25:03.403
He is the reason for this season and wise men still seek him.

25:04.004 --> 25:08.432
Each of us is an innkeeper who decides if there's room in our hearts for him.

25:09.073 --> 25:13.380
He invites us into the puzzle picture, offering peace, salvation and healing.

25:14.222 --> 25:21.394
So no matter how chaotic, deceptive and dangerous the world is becoming, from my heart to yours, the most important question is,

25:21.858 --> 25:25.683
Are you ready for the soon and sudden second appearing of the Lord?

25:26.224 --> 25:28.227
That is our blessed hope.

25:28.487 --> 25:28.868
Amen.

25:29.949 --> 25:34.676
Meanwhile, we'd love to hear from you on social media or through our free Jerusalem channel, mobile app.

25:35.277 --> 25:47.954
Please follow our articles at substack.com and all our videos at our Jerusalem channel, YouTube platform, as well as our website, exploits.tv, where you have the opportunity to support our work financially.

25:48.610 --> 26:07.857
And finally at our website, Contact Page, we invite you to sign up for our weekly email alert called exploits based upon Daniel 1132, declaring the people who know their God will be strong, not weak, and we're going to accomplish biblical exploits, the works of the Lord, in the remaining time before His imminent return.

26:08.738 --> 26:13.565
Meanwhile, let's keep contending for the faith and praying prophetically for the peace of Jerusalem.

26:13.925 --> 26:17.330
I'm Christine Dark, Shalom and Maranatha.

